{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977610/extras/wishlist.png?t=1740239768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977610/extras/BiteFace.gif?t=1740239768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The environment is the main character in this none-survival game. Uncover the tales of the old world as you solve puzzles, platform through overgrown streets and unearth the secrets of people LONG GONE through the belongings left being in a decaying neighbourhood. What will you discover?\u00a0Oh and there's some zombies shuffling around. Watch out for those.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Modern Throwback</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977610/extras/DebzAttack.gif?t=1740239768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>A solo-developer's love letter to retro adventure games, this unique low-poly pixel art game is designed for the controller and brings not only a modern twist with wonderful pixel animation blending a retro-look with a 3D world but also a sense of humor and a much-needed light-heartedness that is juxtaposed against the background of a stark  lost world. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Intimately Unique Environment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1977610/extras/HouseExplore.gif?t=1740239768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a post-apocalyptic neighborhood frozen in time and filled with hundreds of interactive objects that paint a web of a story of the people that once lived there. Featuring an expansive system where you can inspect, carry, combine and interact with hundreds of objects, fully detailed in a unique pixel art low-poly 3D.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <